  "short_description": "AVRACH is a hack&slash game where you can also develop your racing skills using the robot avatar . Odds are stacked against him and strange creatures are challenging his every step, will Avrach ever save his beloved wife? Is he the chosen one? Will he fulfill the prophecy ? Let's play and find out.",
